# myscripts

一行安装(交互安全写法)。脚本作为 `bash -c` 的参数传入,stdin 仍连着终端,
脚本内的 read 提示可正常交互。`--` 后面是传给脚本的命令($1)。

## singbox-install.sh — trojan(TLS) + 明文 SOCKS5
https://raw.githubusercontent.com/olivcraw/myscripts/main/singbox-install.sh

sudo bash -c "$(curl -fsSL https://raw.githubusercontent.com/olivcraw/myscripts/main/singbox-install.sh)" -- install
sudo bash -c "$(curl -fsSL https://raw.githubusercontent.com/olivcraw/myscripts/main/singbox-install.sh)" -- status
sudo bash -c "$(curl -fsSL https://raw.githubusercontent.com/olivcraw/myscripts/main/singbox-install.sh)" -- uninstall

## singbox-monitor.sh — sing-box 健康监控/自愈
https://raw.githubusercontent.com/olivcraw/myscripts/main/singbox-monitor.sh

sudo bash -c "$(curl -fsSL https://raw.githubusercontent.com/olivcraw/myscripts/main/singbox-monitor.sh)" -- install
sudo bash -c "$(curl -fsSL https://raw.githubusercontent.com/olivcraw/myscripts/main/singbox-monitor.sh)" -- check
sudo bash -c "$(curl -fsSL https://raw.githubusercontent.com/olivcraw/myscripts/main/singbox-monitor.sh)" -- status
sudo bash -c "$(curl -fsSL https://raw.githubusercontent.com/olivcraw/myscripts/main/singbox-monitor.sh)" -- uninstall

## ec2-trim.sh — 精简 EC2 系统
https://raw.githubusercontent.com/olivcraw/myscripts/main/ec2-trim.sh

sudo bash -c "$(curl -fsSL https://raw.githubusercontent.com/olivcraw/myscripts/main/ec2-trim.sh)" -- purge
sudo bash -c "$(curl -fsSL https://raw.githubusercontent.com/olivcraw/myscripts/main/ec2-trim.sh)" -- status
sudo bash -c "$(curl -fsSL https://raw.githubusercontent.com/olivcraw/myscripts/main/ec2-trim.sh)" -- restore
